This game has become interesting.

266
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:13,240
I have never treated Xu Duo Cheng and her family as a game.

267
00:15:13,920 --> 00:15:14,980
Why?

268
00:15:14,980 --> 00:15:18,560
Because to me, they are worth cherishing.

269
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:21,680
I won't allow you to hurt them in any way.

270
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:24,640
You cherish them.

271
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:26,360
What about my mom?

272
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:29,260
My mom is also someone I cherish,

273
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:32,400
but you killed her.

274
00:15:36,520 --> 00:15:38,540
If you have any resentment, come at me.

275
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:40,860
What should I do to make you let got of  Xu Duo Cheng?

276
00:15:40,860 --> 00:15:42,800
I won't let her go.

277
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:47,440
I want to make you worry about her every day.

278
00:15:48,060 --> 00:15:49,960
I want to make you unhappy,

279
