I mean your lesson prices are so cheap.

289
00:16:17,660 --> 00:16:19,960
I'm even a little embarrassed.

290
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:21,600
It's good as long as you've learned something.

291
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:25,960
By the way, don't tell Jiang Nan that I came to learn piano.

292
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:28,100
You know him. He's sensitive.

293
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:30,080
I'm afraid he'll misunderstand something.

294
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,320
I won't tell him.

295
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:35,540
 Dad, it's me.

296
00:16:35,540 --> 00:16:36,620
Cheng Cheng?

297
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:38,460
I called you many times but you never answered,

298
00:16:38,460 --> 00:16:39,580
and you didn't even come to the opening ceremony.

299
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:40,880
Where are you doing? Where are you?

300
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:43,700
 Dad, I was giving a piano lesson and couldn't answer the phone,

301
00:16:43,700 --> 00:16:45,160
 and I just got caught in the rain.

302
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:47,720
 I'll get changed and head over, okay?.

303
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,780
What? You could have borrowed someone's phone

304
00:16:49,780 --> 00:16:51,580
and called us to let us know.

305
00:16:51,580 --> 00:16:52,700
We were so worried!

306
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:54,500
 Dad, I was wrong.

307
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:56,840
 I'll go over right now and apologize.

308
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,420
Fine.

309
