I want another piece.

336
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:11,680
Good. I'm afraid you can't have more.

337
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:14,820
The dish is for a customer. I'll cook it for you at home tonight.

338
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:16,160
I'm going to help my mom, then.

339
