You could find anyone to teach you piano.

347
00:19:11,580 --> 00:19:14,600
Why did you have to ask Xu Duo Cheng?

348
00:19:14,600 --> 00:19:18,420
And only after Jiang Nan and her took wedding photos.

349
00:19:21,740 --> 00:19:25,060
I... I just asked her because I knew her.

350
00:19:25,700 --> 00:19:29,600
Gu Jia Yi, I'm warning you again.

351
00:19:30,120 --> 00:19:31,840
Don't mess with Xu Duo Cheng.

352
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:36,040
Otherwise, don't blame me for being rude.

353
00:19:36,760 --> 00:19:39,560
Why are you so angry?

354
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:45,100
And we're two of a kind, aren't we?

355
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:47,180
Stop pretending to be a saint.

356
00:19:47,180 --> 00:19:50,280
You're right but you're wrong.

