00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:55,200
I will compete fairly with Jiang Nan.

358
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:05,860
Cheng Cheng, there was a Xiao Zhan who came to the restaurant today.

359
00:20:05,860 --> 00:20:08,080
Is he pursuing you?

360
00:20:08,660 --> 00:20:10,500
Which Xiao Zhan?

361
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:13,720
That Zhan... Zhan Zhi Lin?

362
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:16,560
He's the owner of the piano store I'm teaching at.

363
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:23,440
Tell Mom the truth. Does he like you?

