00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:26,060
He even told us he was pursuing you.

365
00:20:26,060 --> 00:20:27,480
Don't believe him.

366
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:29,080
It's not true.

367
00:20:29,080 --> 00:20:30,560
Really?

368
00:20:31,120 --> 00:20:34,100
Sweetie, I used to be at your age too.

369
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,500
I understand all of that.

370
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:39,600
You're so beautiful and so cute.

