00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:41,320
It's good for you to have admirers,

372
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:43,380
and I feel very happy too,

373
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:48,480
but Cheng Cheng, since you're dating Jiang Nan,

