426
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:36,780
You're lying, right?

427
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:44,100
Yes.

428
00:24:44,100 --> 00:24:45,840
I like you.

429
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:51,580
But I only like you as your fan.

430
00:24:51,580 --> 00:24:53,360
I'm not into you in real life.

431
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,960
We're not compatible at all.

432
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:51,200
 Jiang Nan, I'm someone without a future.

433
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:54,060
 I can't accompany you through life

434
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:56,620
 and witness your success.

435
00:25:56,620 --> 00:25:59,240
 I can't be your partner for life.

436
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:08,200
 I'm sorry.

437
00:26:57,080 --> 00:26:58,680
You're awake?

438
00:26:59,760 --> 00:27:02,700
You stayed at my door all night?

439
00:27:04,140 --> 00:27:06,000
I didn't dare go sleep in my room.

440
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:08,880
I was afraid you'd pack up your stuff and leave quietly.

441
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:14,120
Don't do that.

442
00:27:20,060 --> 00:27:22,120
I thought all night.

443
00:27:22,120 --> 00:27:27,020
If you think there are still things we need to work through, I'm willing to change for you.

444
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,520
You don't have to change for me.

445
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:31,140
I've really made up my mind already.

446
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:41,540
Hello, Lord Bao.

447
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:43,240
 Hey, Cheng Cheng. Is Lao Jiang there?

448
00:27:43,240 --> 00:27:45,900
 He didn't answer his phone. Are you with him?

449
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:48,160
Wait a sec.

450
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:50,720
It's Lord Bao.

451
00:27:52,600 --> 00:27:55,340
- Hello? 
 - The nursing home staff called you a dozen times, but you didn't answer at all.

452
00:27:55,340 --> 00:27:56,560
They had to call me.

453
00:27:56,560 --> 00:27:58,480
 The address of the nursing home was exposed.

454
00:27:58,480 --> 00:28:00,760
A bunch of reporters are waiting there and want an interview.

455
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:02,200
You better go over and take a look.

456
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:04,520
Got it.

457
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:06,140
I have to go to the nursing home.

458
00:28:06,140 --> 00:28:08,140
Did something happen to Auntie?

459
00:28:09,360 --> 00:28:10,440
Wait at home for me to return.

460
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:11,560
Wait.

461
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:13,180
I'll go with you.

462
00:28:13,180 --> 00:28:15,020
Your mother is going through a critical stage.

463
00:28:15,020 --> 00:28:16,980
She can recognize people once in a while.

464
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:19,400
If she's shocked again, all the progress will be lost.

465
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:21,660
I advise you to move her to another place.

466
00:28:21,660 --> 00:28:24,900
Doctor, my mom once told me she wanted to go back to her hometown.

467
00:28:24,900 --> 00:28:26,320
Do you think it's good for her?

468
00:28:26,320 --> 00:28:27,880
Absolutely.

469
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:31,400
A place she's familiar with is the best.

470
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:33,040
Okay, I see.

471
00:28:33,040 --> 00:28:34,120
Thank you, Doctor.

472
00:28:34,120 --> 00:28:36,380
Thank you for all your help during this time.

473
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:37,980
You're welcome.

474
00:28:45,880 --> 00:28:47,480
Chairman.

475
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:55,100
What has Zhi Lin been doing recently?

476
00:28:55,100 --> 00:28:58,040
Recently, Director Zhan often asks Tao Tao to go to a nursing home.

477
00:28:58,600 --> 00:29:00,000
What?

478
00:29:01,520 --> 00:29:03,220
Ask him to come over here.

479
00:29:03,220 --> 00:29:06,500
Director Zhan went out this afternoon and hasn't returned.

480
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:08,080
- Where did he go? 
 - I don't know.

481
00:29:08,080 --> 00:29:09,580
He didn't mention it.

482
00:29:11,320 --> 00:29:12,480
Get the car ready.

483
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:13,980
Yes, Chairman.

484
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:29,680
Jiang Nan?

485
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:30,700
What are you doing here?

486
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:32,780
You don't think you've hurt my mom enough?

487
00:29:32,780 --> 00:29:34,980
You think this isn't viral enough?

488
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:38,480
I just got the news too.

489
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:41,140
She's doing well. Don't worry.

490
00:29:41,140 --> 00:29:42,940
You may leave.

491
00:29:42,940 --> 00:29:44,560
I...

492
00:29:44,560 --> 00:29:46,500
Could I have a look at her from afar?

493
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:48,780
No need. Please, leave.

494
00:29:51,860 --> 00:29:55,080
Jiang Nan, it's already been so many years.

495
00:29:55,080 --> 00:29:58,493
I've always tried to ease the tension between our two families.

496
00:29:58,493 --> 00:30:01,640
I think this would be good for your mother too.

497
00:30:01,640 --> 00:30:02,920
You don't need to say anything else.

498
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:05,720
All these years, my mother doesn't even recognize me anymore.

499
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:08,060
Let alone, remember you.

500
00:30:09,080 --> 00:30:11,900
So everything you're doing is in vain

501
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:14,600
and will only make you and me suffer more.

502
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:19,740
Then...

503
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:23,600
Could you give your mother this bouquet?

504
00:30:46,880 --> 00:30:48,480
 Where are you?

505
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:49,580
Just tell me what you want to say.

506
00:30:49,580 --> 00:30:52,360
 Did you expose the address of the nursing home where Jiang Nan's mother is?

507
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:53,860
 Why can't you let this go?

508
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:55,960
 Let the past be in the past!

509
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:57,240
Past?

510
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:58,660
How do I let it go?

511
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:01,440
I'm telling you, I'll never let this go!

512
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:26,480
Nan Nan!

513
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:30,060
Our superstar is back!

514
00:31:30,060 --> 00:31:31,860
Aunt.

